*distcc-2.0.1 (31 Mar 2003)

  28 Apr 2003; Zach Welch <zwelch@gentoo.org> distcc-0.12.ebuild,
  distcc-0.12.ebuild, distcc-0.15.ebuild, distcc-0.15.ebuild,
  distcc-1.0.ebuild, distcc-1.0.ebuild, distcc-1.1-r11.ebuild,
